snippet.title: South Park: The Stick of Truth - "Destiny" Trailer
snippet.description: Check out the latest action in South Park: The Stick of Truth by watching the new "Destiny" trailer.  In the trailer, the New Kid steps forth and fulfills his, well, destiny.  South Park: The Stick of Truth, available on December 10 for the PlayStation®3 computer entertainment system, Xbox 360® video game and entertainment system from Microsoft, and Windows PC.
